title: Week 4 Recap 2022
description:
Field Yates, Daniel Dopp and Liz Loza recap everything you need to know from Week 4 of the NFL season including what massive performances are signs of things to come. Plus, audio exclusive reaction to an impressive SNF performance and how you should manage CEH.
